      "updated": 1738805160
    },
    {
      "id": "67a40fa7aff09e000017512b",
      "text": "MCPのResourceはPagenationする想定",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1738805160,
      "updated": 1738805160
    },
    {
      "id": "67a40fa7aff09e000017512c",
      "text": "同じく、いまいち意図が理解できないなぁと思っている[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1738805160,
      "updated": 1738805160
    },
    {
      "id": "67a40fa7aff09e000017512d",
      "text": " リソースが3万件とかあるとレスポンスとして大きすぎるし、それを知らないでListResourcesを叩いたときにどうする想定なんだろうか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1738805160,
      "updated": 1738805160
    },
    {
      "id": "67a40fa7aff09e000017512e",
      "text": " とここまで書いてからドキュメントを読ませてAIに聞こうと思った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1738805160,
      "updated": 1738805160
    },
    {
      "id": "67a40fa7aff09e000017512f",
      "text": " >仕様の以下の記述により、MCPは「大量の結果を小分けにして返す」設計であることが明示されています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1738805160,
      "updated": 1738805160
    },
    {
      "id": "67a40fa7aff09e0000175130",
      "text": " > \"MCP supports paginating list operations that may return large result sets, by yielding results in smaller chunks instead of all at once.\"",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1738805160,
      "updated": 1738805160
    },
    {
      "id": "67a40fa7aff09e0000175131",
      "text": " > [Pagination – Model Context Protocol Specification https://spec.modelcontextprotocol.io/specification/draft/server/utilities/pagination/]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1738805160,
      "updated": 1738805160
    },
    {
      "id": "67a40fa7aff09e0000175132",
